Spool from Outside B (T Spawn)

Paste this in to teleport to exact place/angle.

setpos 2498.968750 -993.968750 1677.927490;setang -29.268682 154.468796 0.000000

Take one step forward then immediately jump throw. If you have made a step noise, you have stepped too far forward. A jump throw bind is recommended to ensure consistency.
